room_title: Escape room "The Father of Silicon Valley" by BreakoutStudios in San Jose
room_description: The “Father of Silicon Valley” has been poisoned! His secret work during WWII to help defeat Germany was uncovered. Without him, the Silicon Valley we know today will not exist. You have 60 minutes to travel back to 1942 break into his home, figure out who poisoned him and find the antidote to save him.
